#sw-explained
  #sw-description
    %p Many teams use chef to manage their production machines, but developers often build their development boxes by hand.  SoloWizard makes it painless to create a customized chef solo script to get your development machine humming: mysql, sublime text, .bash_profile tweaks to OS-X settings - it's all there!
